Heat two tablespoons of olive oil in a large non-stick frying pan. Add the  broccoli florets and sauté for 3-4 minutes, to soften.Add the spring onions and sauté for a further 1-2 minutes.Stir in the mango slices and then add the cooked noodles.Stir in the chilli and continue to stir-fry for a further 3-4 minutes.Finally add the herbs with a tablespoon of olive oil. Heat for another minute and transfer to a serving plate to serve.